  "detailed_description": "<h1>Friend's Pass</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/c0bbed9d5e599a0169aa30552bb23535.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=194 /></span><br><br>Only one of you has to buy the game. Your friends or audience can join for free, up to a total of 8 players. See the download button above to get the Friend's Pass.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/a58a4d23b72535bc707027e9c4ef79d0.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=83 /></span><br><br>Even before the article's topic is revealed, you'll need to come up with words for everyone to play with. Remember, if they're not exciting — no one will want to use them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/8ea1e321299683ab9678b0adfce6ce06.poster.avif?t=1733051184\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/8ea1e321299683ab9678b0adfce6ce06.webm?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/8ea1e321299683ab9678b0adfce6ce06.mp4?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/6fae856c157b15cb8ff669ad695a39d5.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=83 /></span><br><br>Combine the words you're given to create hilarious headlines that fit the news item. Make sure to unleash your creativity because, at this tabloid, truth is negotiable, and humour reigns supreme. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/9fcc4635cf5b377e31c70636cb9240a1.poster.avif?t=1733051184\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/9fcc4635cf5b377e31c70636cb9240a1.webm?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/9fcc4635cf5b377e31c70636cb9240a1.mp4?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/5b993b97bd7edf7583977ac0a39ee078.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=83 /></span><br><br>Brace yourself for the voting stage, where we decide which headline makes the cut. Each player can vote for the funniest and most fitting headline, and the one with the most votes goes straight to press!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/f0097ac86eca4bbb2321e6ca5bbae5ee.poster.avif?t=1733051184\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/f0097ac86eca4bbb2321e6ca5bbae5ee.webm?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/f0097ac86eca4bbb2321e6ca5bbae5ee.mp4?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/a798f585b1a0122e3243b7bb7993a9c0.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=83 /></span><br><br>Then sit back and watch those sweet points roll in. Keep in mind that scoring isn't just about crafting the most popular headline—you'll also earn points for each of your words featured in other players' headlines!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/6214a3f1b54de4ba09e885a574c81bcf.poster.avif?t=1733051184\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/6214a3f1b54de4ba09e885a574c81bcf.webm?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/6214a3f1b54de4ba09e885a574c81bcf.mp4?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/a58a4d23b72535bc707027e9c4ef79d0.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=83 /></span><br><br>Even before the article's topic is revealed, you'll need to come up with words for everyone to play with. Remember, if they're not exciting — no one will want to use them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/8ea1e321299683ab9678b0adfce6ce06.poster.avif?t=1733051184\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/8ea1e321299683ab9678b0adfce6ce06.webm?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/8ea1e321299683ab9678b0adfce6ce06.mp4?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/6fae856c157b15cb8ff669ad695a39d5.avif?t=1733051184\" width=609 height=83 /></span><br><br>Combine the words you're given to create hilarious headlines that fit the news item. Make sure to unleash your creativity because, at this tabloid, truth is negotiable, and humour reigns supreme. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/9fcc4635cf5b377e31c70636cb9240a1.poster.avif?t=1733051184\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850560/extras/9fcc4635cf5b377e31c70636cb9240a1.webm?t=1733051184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass